    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建设你的农场！</h2>○在这个世界中，你可以种植各类农作物、开采矿石、钓鱼和制作等等。○<br>○在不同领域锻炼你的技艺：农业、渔业、战斗、制作、炼金。升级你的技艺，解锁新的能力！<br>○你还可以让各类奇异的生物来帮助你建设你的农场！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161950/extras/298a0ba68680acc1552948bea1f9d92a.poster.avif?t=1772171313\" width=616 height=414 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161950/extras/298a0ba68680acc1552948bea1f9d92a.webm?t=1772171313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161950/extras/298a0ba68680acc1552948bea1f9d92a.mp4?t=1772171313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161950/extras/b2e2558d3267a98265f573bee7b14c2b.poster.avif?t=1772171313\" width=616 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161950/extras/b2e2558d3267a98265f573bee7b14c2b.webm?t=1772171313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161950/extras/b2e2558d3267a98265f573bee7b14c2b.mp4?t=1772171313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在地牢中战斗!</h2>○带上你在农场中合成的各类道具进入地牢，通过打败怪物获得材料和稀有道具！<br>○在地牢中你能遇到各种不同的怪物，有时候你会碰上一些强大的敌人！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161950/extras/f6b5c74daa6f4087e80bfabffd2b90cd.poster.avif?t=1772171313\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161950/extras/f6b5c74daa6f4087e80bfabffd2b90cd.webm?t=1772171313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161950/extras/f6b5c74daa6f4087e80bfabffd2b90cd.mp4?t=1772171313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索新世界!</h2>○这个世界中不同各类的地方。在农场中种植，在矿洞中采矿，在河边垂钓，在地牢中战斗。<br>○结识不同的人物，发展与她们的关系。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161950/extras/328732650d0f003af1b6cef44ca6c158.poster.avif?t=1772171313\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161950/extras/328732650d0f003af1b6cef44ca6c158.webm?t=1772171313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
